-- large LocalScript does not exceed Luau's 200-local-register limit.
function S.initializeLateBuildUI()
	--------------------------------------------------------------------
	-- BUILD FREE-CAM (📷): fly around while building. WASD move, Q/E
	-- down/up, hold RIGHT MOUSE to look, Shift = fast. Tools stay usable.
	-- v9: the camera render loop only EXISTS while flying.
	--------------------------------------------------------------------
